OL,7,BSeal's your man for film soundtracks at
OL,8,Bthe moment, it seems. Not content with 
OL,9,BBatman, he's gone and had a go at a    
OL,10,Btune by the Steve Miller Band for new  
OL,11,Bflick Space Jam. Its fate as a hit is  
OL,12,Bmost definitely, er, Sealed.E      
